{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Sustainability represents"},{"time":2000,"text":"the what, the where and the how"},{"time":4000,"text":"of what is caught."},{"time":6000,"text":"The who and the why are what's important to me."},{"time":8000,"text":"I want to know the people behind my dinner choices."},{"time":10000,"text":"I want to know how I impact them."},{"time":12000,"text":"I want to know how they impact me."},{"time":14000,"text":"I want to know why they fish."},{"time":16000,"text":"I want to know how they rely on the water's bounty"},{"time":18000,"text":"for their living."},{"time":20000,"text":"Understanding all of this enables us"},{"time":22000,"text":"to shift our perception of seafood"},{"time":24000,"text":"away from a commodity"},{"time":26000,"text":"to an opportunity"},{"time":28000,"text":"to restore our ecosystem."},{"time":30000,"text":"It allows for us to celebrate the seafood"},{"time":32000,"text":"that we're also so fortunate to eat."}]},{"cues":[{"time":34000,"text":"So what do we call this?"},{"time":36000,"text":"I think we call it restorative seafood."},{"time":39000,"text":"Where sustainability is the capacity"},{"time":41000,"text":"to endure and maintain,"},{"time":43000,"text":"restorative is the ability to replenish and progress."},{"time":46000,"text":"Restorative seafood allows for an evolving and dynamic system"},{"time":49000,"text":"and acknowledges our relationship with the ocean"},{"time":51000,"text":"as a resource,"},{"time":53000,"text":"suggesting that we engage to replenish the ocean"},{"time":56000,"text":"and to encourage its resiliency."},{"time":58000,"text":"It is a more hopeful, it is a more human,"},{"time":61000,"text":"and is a more useful way of understanding our environment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":65000,"text":"Wallet guides -- standard issue"},{"time":68000,"text":"by lots in the marine conservation world --"},{"time":70000,"text":"are very handy; they're a wonderful tool."},{"time":73000,"text":"Green, yellow and red lists [of] seafood species."},{"time":76000,"text":"The association is very easy: buy green, don't buy red,"},{"time":79000,"text":"think twice about yellow."},{"time":81000,"text":"But in my mind, it's really not enough"},{"time":83000,"text":"to just eat green list."},{"time":85000,"text":"We can't sustain this without the measure of our success"},{"time":88000,"text":"really changing the fate of the species"},{"time":90000,"text":"in the yellow and the red."},{"time":92000,"text":"But what if we eat only in the green list?"},{"time":95000,"text":"You've got pole-caught yellowfin tuna here --"},{"time":98000,"text":"comes from sustainable stocks."},{"time":100000,"text":"Pole caught -- no bycatch."},{"time":102000,"text":"Great for fishermen. Lots of money. Supporting local economies."},{"time":105000,"text":"But it's a lion of the sea. It's a top predator."}]},{"cues":[{"time":108000,"text":"What's the context of this meal?"},{"time":110000,"text":"Am I sitting down in a steakhouse to a 16-ounce portion of this?"},{"time":113000,"text":"Do I do this three times a week?"},{"time":115000,"text":"I might still be in the green list,"},{"time":117000,"text":"but I'm not doing myself, or you,"},{"time":119000,"text":"or the oceans any favors."},{"time":123000,"text":"The point is that we have to have a context,"},{"time":125000,"text":"a gauge for our actions in all this."},{"time":128000,"text":"Example: I've heard that red wine is great for my health --"},{"time":131000,"text":"antioxidants and minerals -- heart healthy."},{"time":133000,"text":"That's great! I love red wine!"},{"time":135000,"text":"I'm going to drink so much of it. I'm going to be so healthy."},{"time":138000,"text":"Well, how many bottles is it"},{"time":140000,"text":"before you tell me that I have a problem?"},{"time":142000,"text":"Well folks, we have a protein problem."},{"time":144000,"text":"We have lost this sensibility"},{"time":146000,"text":"when it regards our food,"},{"time":148000,"text":"and we are paying a cost."},{"time":150000,"text":"The problem is we are hiding that cost beneath the waves."},{"time":153000,"text":"We are hiding that cost"},{"time":155000,"text":"behind the social acceptance of expanding waistlines."},{"time":157000,"text":"And we are hiding that cost behind monster profits."}]},{"cues":[{"time":161000,"text":"So the first thing about this idea of restorative seafood"},{"time":163000,"text":"is that it really takes into account our needs."},{"time":166000,"text":"Restorative seafood might best be represented"},{"time":168000,"text":"not by Jaws, or by Flipper, or the Gordon's fisherman,"},{"time":170000,"text":"but rather, by the Jolly Green Giant."},{"time":173000,"text":"Vegetables:"},{"time":175000,"text":"they might yet save the oceans."},{"time":177000,"text":"Sylvia likes to say that blue is the new green."},{"time":179000,"text":"Well I'd like to respectfully submit"},{"time":181000,"text":"that broccoli green might then be the new blue."},{"time":185000,"text":"We must continue to eat"},{"time":187000,"text":"the best seafood possible, if at all."},{"time":190000,"text":"But we also must eat it with a ton of vegetables."},{"time":193000,"text":"The best part about restorative seafood though"},{"time":195000,"text":"is that it comes on the half-shell"},{"time":197000,"text":"with a bottle of Tabasco and lemon wedges."},{"time":199000,"text":"It comes in a five-ounce portion of tilapia"},{"time":201000,"text":"breaded with Dijon mustard and crispy, broiled breadcrumbs"},{"time":204000,"text":"and a steaming pile of pecan quinoa pilaf"},{"time":206000,"text":"with crunchy, grilled broccoli"},{"time":208000,"text":"so soft and sweet and charred and smoky on the outside"},{"time":210000,"text":"with just a hint of chili flake."},{"time":212000,"text":"Whooo!"},{"time":214000,"text":"This is an easy sell."},{"time":216000,"text":"And the best part is all of those ingredients are available"},{"time":218000,"text":"to every family at the neighborhood Walmart."}]},{"cues":[{"time":221000,"text":"Jamie Oliver is campaigning"},{"time":224000,"text":"to save America from the way we eat."},{"time":227000,"text":"Sylvia is campaigning to save the oceans"},{"time":230000,"text":"from the way we eat."},{"time":232000,"text":"There's a pattern here."},{"time":234000,"text":"Forget nuclear holocaust;"},{"time":236000,"text":"it's the fork that we have to worry about."},{"time":239000,"text":"We have ravaged our Earth"},{"time":241000,"text":"and then used the food that we've sourced"},{"time":243000,"text":"to handicap ourselves in more ways than one."},{"time":246000,"text":"So I think we have this whole eating thing wrong."},{"time":249000,"text":"And so I think it's time"},{"time":251000,"text":"we change what we expect from our food."},{"time":253000,"text":"Sustainability is complicated"},{"time":255000,"text":"but dinner is a reality that we all very much understand."},{"time":258000,"text":"So let's start there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":260000,"text":"There's been a lot of movement recently in greening our food systems."},{"time":263000,"text":"Dan Barber and Alice Waters"},{"time":265000,"text":"are leading passionately the green food Delicious Revolution."},{"time":268000,"text":"But green foods often represent"},{"time":270000,"text":"a way for us to disregard"},{"time":272000,"text":"the responsibility as eaters."},{"time":274000,"text":"Just because it comes from a green source"},{"time":276000,"text":"doesn't mean we can treat it with disregard on the plate."},{"time":280000,"text":"We have eco-friendly shrimp."},{"time":282000,"text":"We can make them; we have that technology."},{"time":284000,"text":"But we can never have any eco-friendly all-you-can-eat shrimp buffet."},{"time":288000,"text":"It doesn't work."},{"time":290000,"text":"Heart-healthy dinner is a very important part"},{"time":293000,"text":"of restorative seafood."},{"time":295000,"text":"While we try to manage declining marine populations,"},{"time":298000,"text":"the media's recommending increased consumption of seafood."},{"time":301000,"text":"Studies say that tens of thousands"},{"time":303000,"text":"of American grandmothers, grandfathers, mothers and fathers"},{"time":305000,"text":"might be around for another birthday"},{"time":307000,"text":"if we included more seafood."},{"time":309000,"text":"That's a reward I am not willing to pass up."},{"time":312000,"text":"But it's not all about the seafood."},{"time":314000,"text":"It's about the way that we look at our plates."}]},{"cues":[{"time":317000,"text":"As a chef, I realize the easiest thing for me to do"},{"time":319000,"text":"is reduce the portion sizes on my plate."},{"time":322000,"text":"A couple things happened."},{"time":324000,"text":"I made more money."},{"time":326000,"text":"People started buying appetizers and salads,"},{"time":328000,"text":"because they knew they weren't going to fill up on the entrees alone."},{"time":331000,"text":"People spent more time engaging in their meals,"},{"time":333000,"text":"engaging with each other over their meals."},{"time":336000,"text":"People got, in short, more of what they came there for"},{"time":339000,"text":"even though they got less protein."},{"time":341000,"text":"They got more calories over the course of a diversified meal."},{"time":344000,"text":"They got healthier. I made more money."},{"time":346000,"text":"This is great."},{"time":348000,"text":"Environmental consideration was served with every plate,"},{"time":351000,"text":"but it was served with a heaping mound"},{"time":353000,"text":"of consideration for human interests at the same time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":357000,"text":"One of the other things we did"},{"time":359000,"text":"was begin to diversify the species that we served --"},{"time":362000,"text":"small silverfish, anchovies, mackerel, sardines were uncommon."},{"time":365000,"text":"Shellfish, mussels, oysters,"},{"time":367000,"text":"clams, tilapia, char -- these were the common species."},{"time":370000,"text":"We were directing tastes"},{"time":372000,"text":"towards more resilience, more restorative options."},{"time":376000,"text":"This is what we need to favor."},{"time":378000,"text":"This is what the green list says."},{"time":380000,"text":"But this is also how we can actually begin to restore our environment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":383000,"text":"But what of those big predators,"},{"time":385000,"text":"those fashionable species,"},{"time":387000,"text":"that green list tuna that I was talking about earlier?"},{"time":390000,"text":"Well, if you must, I have a recipe for you."},{"time":393000,"text":"It pretty much works with any big fish in the ocean,"},{"time":395000,"text":"so here we go."},{"time":397000,"text":"Start with a 16-ounce portion of big fish."},{"time":400000,"text":"Get a knife. Cut it into four portions."},{"time":403000,"text":"Put it on four plates."},{"time":405000,"text":"Mound up those four plates with vegetables"},{"time":407000,"text":"and then open up the very best bottle of Burgundy you have,"},{"time":409000,"text":"light the candles and celebrate it."},{"time":412000,"text":"Celebrate the opportunity you have to eat this."},{"time":414000,"text":"Invite your friends and neighbors over"},{"time":416000,"text":"and repeat once a year,"},{"time":419000,"text":"maybe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":421000,"text":"I expect a lot from food."},{"time":423000,"text":"I expect health"},{"time":425000,"text":"and joy and family and community."},{"time":427000,"text":"I expect that producing ingredients,"},{"time":429000,"text":"preparing dishes and eating meals"},{"time":432000,"text":"is all part of the communion of human interests."},{"time":435000,"text":"I was lucky enough that my father was a fantastic cook."},{"time":437000,"text":"And he taught me very early on"},{"time":439000,"text":"about the privilege that eating represents."},{"time":442000,"text":"I remember well the meals of my childhood."},{"time":444000,"text":"They were reasonable portions of protein"},{"time":446000,"text":"served with copious quantities of vegetables"},{"time":448000,"text":"and small amounts of starch, usually rice."},{"time":450000,"text":"This is still how I largely eat today."},{"time":453000,"text":"I get sick when I go to steakhouses."},{"time":456000,"text":"I get the meat sweats."},{"time":458000,"text":"It's like a hangover from protein."},{"time":460000,"text":"It's disgusting."},{"time":463000,"text":"But of all the dire news that you'll hear"},{"time":466000,"text":"and that you have heard about the state of our oceans,"},{"time":468000,"text":"I have the unfortunate burden of delivering to you"},{"time":470000,"text":"possibly the very worst of it"},{"time":472000,"text":"and that is this whole time"},{"time":474000,"text":"your mother was right."},{"time":476000,"text":"Eat your vegetables."},{"time":479000,"text":"It's pretty straightforward."}]},{"cues":[{"time":481000,"text":"So what are we looking for in a meal?"},{"time":483000,"text":"Well for health, I'm looking for wholesome ingredients"},{"time":486000,"text":"that are good for my body."},{"time":488000,"text":"For joy, I'm looking for butter and salt"},{"time":490000,"text":"and sexy things that make things taste less like penance."},{"time":493000,"text":"For family, I'm looking for recipes"},{"time":496000,"text":"that genuflect to my own personal histories."},{"time":499000,"text":"For community though, we start at the very beginning."},{"time":502000,"text":"There's no escaping the fact"},{"time":504000,"text":"that everything we eat has a global impact."},{"time":506000,"text":"So try and learn as best you can what that impact is"},{"time":508000,"text":"and then take the first step to minimize it."},{"time":512000,"text":"We've seen an image of our blue planet,"},{"time":514000,"text":"our world bank."},{"time":516000,"text":"But it is more than just a repository of our resources;"},{"time":519000,"text":"it's also the global geography"},{"time":522000,"text":"of the communion we call dinner."},{"time":525000,"text":"So if we all take only what we need,"},{"time":527000,"text":"then we can begin to share the rest,"},{"time":530000,"text":"we can begin to celebrate,"},{"time":532000,"text":"we can begin to restore."},{"time":534000,"text":"We need to savor vegetables."},{"time":536000,"text":"We need to savor smaller portions of seafood."},{"time":539000,"text":"And we need to save dinner."}]},{"cues":[{"time":541000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":543000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}